text: The Škoda Yeti is an SUV car produced by Škoda Auto since 2009. It was facelifted in 2013 and its boxy styling received mixed reviews. It has been replaced in late 2017 by a new, normal looking model called the Karoq. == Engines == * 1.2 TSI 77 kW (105 hp) * 1.8 TSI 118 kW (160 hp) * 2.0 TDI 81 kW (110 hp), 103 kW (140 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) Yeti Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles Category:Sport utility vehicles
title: Škoda Yeti
